<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") -%>

<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 px-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">About VistaGo</h1>
            <p class="text-muted fs-5">Connecting travelers with unique stays and experiences across the globe.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            
            <div class="legal-content fs-6 lh-lg">
                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Mission</h4>
                    <p>At VistaGo, our mission is to make travel accessible, immersive, and unforgettable. We believe that every journey should be more than just a trip—it should be an experience that stays with you forever. By connecting guests with passionate hosts, we create a world where everyone can belong anywhere.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">The VistaGo Experience</h4>
                    <p>From cozy mountain cabins to modern city lofts, VistaGo offers a diverse range of properties tailored to every traveler's needs. We prioritize safety, comfort, and authenticity, ensuring that every listing on our platform meets the high standards our community expects.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Core Values</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We strive to build a community where everyone feels welcome.</li>
                        <li><strong>Trust & Safety:</strong> We implement rigorous verification processes for both hosts and guests.</li>
                        <li><strong>Passion for Travel:</strong> We are a team of travelers building for travelers.</li>
                        <li><strong>Local Impact:</strong> We support local economies by promoting sustainable tourism.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5 text-center bg-light p-4 rounded-4">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Ready to start your adventure?</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4">Join thousands of travelers who have found their perfect home away from home with VistaGo.</p>
                    <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-brand px-5 py-3 rounded-3 fw-bold text-white">Explore Listings</a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
